hadiths[43]{hadithnumber,text}:
2645,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jiskey sath Allah bhalai ka irada farmata hai, to usey Deen ki samajh ata kar deta hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Abu-Hurera , aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2646,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo ilm hasil karney key iradey sey kahin jaey, to Allah uskey liye jannat key raastey ko aasan (o humwaar) kar deta hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2647,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs ilm hasil karney key liye nikley to wo lotney tak Allah ki raah mein) shumar ( hoga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney isey ghair marfoo riwayat kya hai."
2648,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo ilm hasil kerega to ye uskey pichley gunahon ka kaffara bin jaeyga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad zaeef hai, 2- Raavi abu-Daawood Nufey Aama hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain, 3- hum Abdullah bin sakhbara sey marvi ziyada hadisein nahin jantey aur na unkey baap ki) yani ye dono baap betey ghair maroof qism key log hain ( , abu-Daawood ka naam Nufey Aama hai. unkey barey mein Qatada aur doosrey bahut sey ehle-ilm ney kalam kya hai."
2649,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis sey ilme-deen ki koi aisi baat poochhi jaey jisey wo janta hai, phir wo usey chupaey to qiyamat key din usey aag ki lagaam pahnaai jaeygi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2650,"hum abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) key paas (ilme-deen hasil karney key liye) aatey , to wo kehtey : Allah key Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wasiyat key mutabiq tumhen khush aamadeed, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' log tumharey peechey hain padhi. kuch log tumharey paas zamin key goshey goshey sey ilme-deen hasil karney key liye ayengey to jab wo tumharey paas ayen to tum unkey sath bhalai karna''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali bin Abdullah bin al-Madini ney kaha : Yahya bin Saeed kehtey they : Shoba Abu-Harun Abdi ko zaeef qarar detey they, 2- Yahya bin Saeed kehtey hain : ibne-Aun jab tak zinda rahey hamesha Abu-Harun Abdi sey riwayat kartey rahey, 3- Abu-Harun ka naam Imaara bin Juwen hai."
2651,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumharey paas purab sey log ilm hasil karney key liye ayengey pas jab wo tumharey paas ayen to unkey sath bhalai karna''. Raavi hadees kehtey hain : abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ka haal ye tha ke jab wo hamen (taalibaane-ilme-deen ko) dekhtey to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wasiyat key mutabiq hamen khush aamadeed kehtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hum is hadees ko sirf Abu-Harun ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur wo abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain.
2652,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ilm is tarah nahin uthaeyga ke usey logon key seenon sey khinch ley, lekin wo ilm ko ulama ki wafat key zariey sey uthaeyga, yahan tak ke jab wo kisi aalim ko baqi nahin rakhega to log apna sardar jahilon ko bana leingey, un sey masley puchey jaeyngey to wo baghair ilm key fatwey dengey, wo khud gumrah hongey aur dusron ko bhi gumrah kerengey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Zohri ney Urwa sey aur Urwa ney Abdullah bin Amr sey riwayat ki hai, aur Zohri ney (eik dusri sanad sey) Urwa sey aur Urwa ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Aaisha aur Ziyad bin Labid sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2653,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they, achcha aap ney apni nazren aasman par gaad din, phir farmaya : '' aisa waqt ( aa gaya ( hai ke jis mein logon key seenon sey ilm uchak liya jaeyga. yahan tak ke logon key paas kuch bhi ilm nahin hoga, Ziyad bin Labid Ansari ney kaha : ( Allah key Rasool ! ( ilm hum sey kis tarah chin liya jaeyga jabke hum Quran padhtey hongey. qism Allah ki ! hum zarur usey padheingey aur hum zarur apni aurton ko usey padhaeingey aur apney bachon ko sikhaeingey. aap ney farmaya : '' aey Ziyad tumhari maa tumhen kho dey ! main to tumhen ehal Madina key fuqaha mein sey shumar karta tha. ye Torat aur Injeel bhi to paas hai Yahud o Nasara key kya kaam aai unkey ? '' padhi. ( kya faeyda pahunchaya Torat aur Injeel ney in ko ? ( . Juber ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : meri mulaqat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey hui to mainey un sey kaha : kya aap nahin suntey ke aap key bhai Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) kya kehtey hain? phir Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney jo kaha tha wo mainey unhen bata diya . unhoney kaha : Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney sach kaha . aur agar tum ( mazeed ( janna chaho to main tumhen bata sakta hun ke pehley pehal logon sey utha liya janey wala ilm , khushu hai. anqarib aisa waqt aayega ke tum jaamaa masjid key andar jaaogey lekin wahan tumhen koi (sahih maanon mein) khushu khuzoo apnaney wala shakhs dikhai na dega. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Muawiya bin Saleh muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa hain. aur Yahya bin Saeed Qataan key siwa hum kisi ko nahin jantey ke usney unkey mutalliq kuch kalam kya ho, 3- Muawiya bin Saleh sey bhi isi tarah ki hadees marvi hai, 4- baazon ney ye hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Juber bin Nufer sey, Abdur-Rehman ney apney walid Juber sey, Juber ney Auf bin Malik sey aur Auf bin Malik ney bani akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
2654,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' jo shakhs ilm is wastey seekhey ke uskey zariey ulama ki barabari karey padhi. , kam ilm aur bewaqufon sey behes o takraar karey ya us ilm key zariey logon ko apna garwida bana ley to aisey shakhs ko Allah Taala jahannam mein dakhil farmaeyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 3- Is-haq bin Yahya bin Talha muhaddeseen key nazdik kuch bahut ziyada qawi nahin hain, unkey hafizey key silsiley mein kalam kya gaya hai."
2655,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney ilm ko ghairullah key liye seekha ya wo us ilm key zariey Allah ki raza key bajaey kuch aur hasil karna chahta hai to aisa shakhs apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- hum isey Ayub ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Jabir sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2656,"Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) dopahar key waqt Marwan key paas sey nikley ( lotey ( , hamney kaha : Marwan ko unsey koi chiz poochhna hogi tabhi in ko us waqt bula bheja hoga, phir hamney un sey puchha to unhoney kaha : haan , unhoney hum sey kaee cheezein poochin jisey hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna tha. mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' Allah us shakhs ko tar-o-taza rakhey jo mujh sey koi hadees suney phir usey yad rakh kar usey dusron ko pahuncha dey , kyonkey bahut sey ehkam shariaa ka ilm rakhney waley us ilm ko us tak pahuncha detey hain jo us sey ziyada zi ilm aur aqlmand hotey hain. aur bahut sey shariyat ka ilm rakhney waley ilm to rakhtey hain, lekin faqeeh nahin hotey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Sabit ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Muaz bin Jabal , Juber bin Mut-im , Abu-Darda aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2657,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' Allah us shakhs ko tar-o-taza (aur khush ( rakhey jisney mujh sey koi baat suni phir usney usey jaisa kuch mujh sey suna tha hu-bahu dusron tak pahuncha diya kyonkey bahut sey log jinhen baat ( hadees) pahunchaai jaey pahunchaney waley sey kahin ziyada baat ko tawajjoh sey sunney aur mehfooz rakhney waley hotey hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is hadees ko abdul-Malik bin Umer ney Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah key wastey sey bayan kya."
2658,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah us shakhs ko tar-o-taza rakhey jo meri baat ko suney aur tawajjoh sey suney , usey mehfooz rakhey aur dusron tak pahunchaey, kyonkey bahut sey ilm ki samajh rakhney waley ilm ko us tak pahuncha detey hain jo un sey ziyada soojh-bojh rakhtey hain. teen cheezen aisi hain jinki wajeh sey eik musalman ka dil dhoka nahin kha sakta, (1) amal khalis Allah key liye (2) musalmanon key aimma key sath khair-khahi (3) aur musalmanon ki jamaat sey judkar rehna, kyonkey dawat unka chaaron taraf sey ihata karti hai''."
2659,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney jaan-bojh kar meri taraf jhoot ki nisbat ki to wo jahannam mein apna thikana bana ley '' padhi. .
2660,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mujh par jhoot na baandho kyonkey mujh par jhoot baandhney wala jahannam mein dakhil hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar, Umar, Usman, Zuber, Saeed bin Zaid, Abdullah bin Amr , Anas , Jabir , ibne-Abbas , abu-Saeed , Amr bin Abasa , Aqba bin Aamir , Muawiya , Barida , abu-Musa , abu-Umama , Abdullah bin umr , Miqna aur Aus Saqafi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2661,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney merey mutalliq jhooti baat kahi '' , ( Anas kehtey hain ( mera khayal hai ke aap ney (من كذب علي) key baad « متعمدا » ka lafz bhi kaha yani jisney jaan-bujh kar mujh par jhoot baandha,'' to aisey shakhs ka thikana jahannam hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. yani Zohri ki us riwayat sey jisey wo Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, 2- ye hadees mutaaddid sanadon sey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai."
2662,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney meri taraf mansub kar key jaan-bujh kar koi jhooti hadees bayan ki to wo do jhoot bolney walon mein sey eik hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shoba ney hukm sey, Hakam ney Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila sey , Abdur-Rehman ney Samra sey , aur Samra ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye hadees riwayat ki hai, 3- Aamash aur ibne-Abi Leila ney Hakam sey, Hakam ney Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila sey, Abdur-Rehman ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, aur Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila ki hadees jisey wo Samra sey riwayat kartey hain, muhaddeseen key nazdik ziyada sahih hai, 4- is bab mein Ali ibne-Abi Talib aur Samra Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 5- mainey abu Muhammad Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees ( من حدث عني حديثا وهو يرى أنه كذب فهو أحد الكاذبين) key mutalliq puchha ke us sey murad kya hai, mainey un sey kaha kya ke jisney koi hadees bayan ki aur wo janta hai ke uski asnaad mein kuch khata ( ghalati aur kami ( hai to kya ye khof o khatra mehsus kya jaey ke aisa shakhs Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki is hadees ki zad aur waeed mein aa gaya. ya us sey murad ye hai ke logon ney hadees mursal bayan ki to unhi mein sey kuch logon ney us mursal ko marfoo kar diya ya uski asnaad ko hi ulat palat diya to ye log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki is hadees ki zad mein ayengey? to unhoney kaha : nahin, uska maana ( o matlab) ye hai ke jab koi shakhs hadees riwayat karey aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tak is hadees key marfoo honey ki koi asal (wajeh o sabab) na jaani jati ho, aur wo shakhs usey marfoo karkey bayan kar dey ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisa farmaya ya aisa kya hai to mujhey dar hai ke aisa hi shakhs is hadees ka misdaaq hoga ."
2663,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main tum mein sey kisi ko hergiz us haal mein na paaun ke wo apney aarasta takht par tek lagaey ho aur uskey paas merey Amr ya nahi ki qism ka koi hukm pahunchey to wo ye kahey ke main kuch nahin janta, hamney to Allah ki kitab mein jo chiz pai uski perwi ki''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz raawiyon ney Sufiyan sey , Sufiyan ney ibn Munkadir sey aur ibn Munkadir ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is hadees ko mursalan riwayat kya hai. aur baaz ney ye hadees Salim Abu-Nazar sey, Salim ney Ubedullah bin abu-Raafey sey, Ubedullah ney apney walid abu-Raafey sey aur abu-Raafey ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 3- ibne-Uena jab is hadees ko alehda bayan kartey they to Muhammad bin Munkadir ki hadees ko Salim bin Nazar ki hadees sey juda juda bayan kartey they aur jab dono hadeeson ko jama kar detey to isi tarah riwayat kartey ( jaisa ke is hadees mein hai) 4- abu-Raafey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key azad karda ghulam hain aur unka naam Aslam hai."
2664,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khabrdar raho ! qarib hai ke koi aadmi apney aarasta takht par tek lagaey betha ho aur wo kahey : hamarey aur tumharey darmiyan ( faisley ki chiz ( bas Allah ki kitab hai. is mein jo chiz hum halal paeyngey pas usi ko halal samjhengey, aur is mein jo chiz haram paeyngey bas usi ko hum haram janengey, yad rakho ! bila shak o shubha Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jo chiz haram qarar dey di hai wo wesay hi haram hai jaisey ke Allah ki haram ki hui chiz ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
2665,"hamney (ibtida Islam mein) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ilm ( hadees ( likh leney ki ijazat talab ki to aap ney hamen likhney ki ijazat na di padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi Zaid bin Aslam key wastey sey aai hai, aur usey Hamaam ney Zaid bin Aslam sey riwayat kya hai."
2666,"eik Ansari shakhs Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki majlis mein betha karta tha. wo aap ki hadisein sunta aur ye hadisein usey bahut pasand aati thin, lekin wo unhen yad nahin rakh paata tha to usney apney yad na rakh paney ki Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey shikayat ki. usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main aap ki hadisein sunta hun aur wo mujhey bahut achi lagti hain ( magar ( main unhen yad nahin rakh paata hun. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum apney dahiney haath ka sahara lo (aur ye kehtey huye ( aapney haath sey likh leney ka ishara farmaya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad qawi o mustehkam nahin hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail ko kehtey huye suna : khaleel bin Murra munkirul-hadees hai, 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2667,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khutba diya aur dorane-khutba aap ney koi qissa ( koi waqia ( bayan kya to abu Shah ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! merey liye likhwa dijiye (yani kisi sey likha dijiye ( to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ( Sahaba sey) kaha abu Shah key liye likh do . hadees mein pura waqia mazkur hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sheban ney Yahya bin abi Kasir sey usi jaisi riwayat bayan ki hai."
2668,"mainey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huye suna ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba mein siwaye Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) key Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadees bayan karney wala mujh sey ziyada koi nahin hai aur merey aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) key darmiyan ye farq tha ke wo ( ahadees ( likh letey they aur main likhta nahin tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur riwayat mein (وهب بن منبه ، an أخيه) jo aaya , to « أخيه » sey murad Hamam bin munabba hain."
2669,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' meri taraf sey logon ko (ehkame-Ilaahi) pahuncha do agar-che eik aayat hi ho, aur bani-Israel sey bayan karo, un sey bayan karney mein koi harj nahin, aur jisney jaan-bojh kar meri taraf kisi jhoot ki nisbat ki to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2670,"eik shakhs Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas sawari maangney aaya, to aap key paas usey koi sawari na mili jo usey manzile-maqsood tak pahuncha deti. aap ney usey eik doosrey shakhs key paas bhej diya, usney usey sawari faraham kar di. phir usney aa kar aap ko uski ittilaa di to aap ney farmaya : '' bhalai ki taraf rehnumai karney wala ( sawab mein) bhalai karney waley hi ki tarah hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey yani Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey jisey wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Masood Badri aur Barida Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2671,"eik shakhs Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas sawari maangney aaya, aur kaha : main be-sawari key ho gaya hun to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey kaha : ''tum falan shakhs key paas jaao '' , chunanche wo us shakhs key paas gaya aur usney isey sawari dey di to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney bhalai ka raasta dikhaya to usey itna hi ajr milta hai jitna ke uskey karney waley ko milta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur abu-Masood Badri ka naam Aqba bin Amr hai."
2672,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shafaat (sifarish) karo taake ajr paao , Allah apney Nabi ki zaban sey nikli hui jis baat ( jis sifarish ( ko bhi chahta hai pura kar deta hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2673,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zulm sey jo bhi khoon hota hai us khoon key gunah ka eik hissey Adam key ( pehley ( betey par jata hai, kyonkey usi ney sab sey pehley khoon karney ki sabeel nikali '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2674,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney logon ko hidayat ki taraf bulaya to jo log uski perwi kerengey unkey ajr key barabar hidayat ki taraf bulaney waley ko bhi sawab milega baghair uskey ke uski ittiba karney walon key ajr o sawab mein kuch bhi kami ho, aur jisney gumrahi ki taraf bulaya to jo log uski perwi kerengey unkey gunahon key barabar gumrahi ki taraf bulaney waley ko bhi gunah milega baghair uskey ke uski wajeh sey unkey gunahon mein sey kuch bhi kami ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2675,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney koi achcha tariqa jari kya (koi achi sunnat qaaim ki) aur us achey tareeqey ki perwi ki gaee to usey (eik to) usey apney amal ka ajr milega aur (doosrey) jo uski perwi kerengey unkey ajr o sawab mein kisi tarah ki kami kiye baghair unkey ajr o sawab key barabar bhi usey sawab milega , aur jisney koi bura tariqa jari kya aur us burey tareeqey ki perwi ki gaee to eik to is par apney amal ka bojh ( gunah ( hoga aur) doosrey ( jo log uski perwi kerengey unkey gunahon key barabar bhi usi par gunah hoga, baghair uskey ke uski perwi karney walon key gunahon mein koi kami ki gaee ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Jareer bin Abdullah sey aai hai, aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- ye hadees munzir bin Jareer bin Abdullah sey bhi aai hai, jisey wo apney walid Jareer bin Abdullah sey aur Jareer Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, 4- ye hadees Ubedullah bin Jareer sey bhi aai hai, aur Ubedullah apney walid Jareer sey aur Jareer ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, 5- is bab mein Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2676,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik din hamen namaz Fajr key baad eik muassar nasihat farmaai jis sey logon ki aankhen aansuon sey bheeg gaeen aur dil laraz gaey, eik shakhs ney kaha : ye nasihat aisi hai jaisi nasihat duniya sey) aakhiri baar ( rukhsat ho kar janey waley kya kartey hain, to Allah key Rasool! aap hamen kis baat ki wasiyat kartey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''main tum logon ko Allah sey dartey rehney, ameer ki baat sunney aur usey manney ki nasihat karta hun, agar-che tumhara Haakim aur ameer eik Habshi ghulam hi kyon na ho, kyonkey tum mein sey aainda jo zinda rahega wo (ummat key andar) bahut sarey ikhtilafat dekhega to tum (baqi rehney walon) ko meri wasiyat hai ke naey-naey fitnon aur naee-naee bidaton mein na padna, kyonkey ye sab gumrahi hain. chunanche tum mein sey jo shakhs un halaat ko paaley to usey chahiye ke wo meri aur merey hidayat yafta khulafaey-Rashedin ki sunnat par qaaim aur jama rahey aur meri us nasihat ko apney daanton key zariey mazbooti sey daba ley ''. (aur is par amal paira rahey (Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sor bin Yazeed ney b-sanad (خالد بن معدان an عبدالرحمٰن بن عمرو السلمي an العرباض بن سارية an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
2677,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Bilal bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : ''samajh lo'' (jaan lo) unhoney kaha : samajhney aur janney ki chiz kya hai? Allah key Rasool! aap ney farmaya : ''samajh lo aur jaan lo'', unhoney arz kya : samajhney aur janney ki chiz kya hai? Allah key Rasool! aap ney farmaya : ''jisney meri kisi aisi sunnat ko zinda kya jis par logon ney merey baad amal karna chhod diya hai, to usey itna sawab milega jitna ke us sunnat par amal karney walon ko milega , ye unkey ajron mein sey kuch bhi kami nahin kerega, aur jisney gumrahi ki koi naee bidat nikali jissey Allah aur uska Rasool razi o khush nahin, to usey is par amal karney walon key gunahon key barabar gunah hoga, uskey gunahon mein sey kuch bhi kami nahin kerega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Muhammad bin Uena Musesi Shaami hain, 3- aur Kasir bin Abdullah sey murad Kasir bin Abdullah bin Amr bin Auf Muzni hain."
2678,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey betey : agar tum sey ho sakey ke subh o Sham tum is tarah guzaarey ke tumharey dil mein kisi key liye bhi khot ( bughz , hasad , keena waghera) na ho to aisa kar liya karo '' , phir aap ney farmaya : '' merey betey ! aisa karna meri sunnat (aur mera tariqa ( hai, aur jisney meri sunnat ko zinda kya usney mujh sey mohabbat ki aur jisney mujh sey mohabbat ki wo merey sath jannat mein rahega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees main eik lamba qissa bhi hai, 2- is sanad sey ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 3- Muhammad bin Abdullah Ansari Suqa hain, aur unkey baap bhi Suqa hain, 4- Ali bin Zaid Sadooq hain ( unka shumar sahon mein hai) bas un mein itni si kami o kharabi hai ke wo kabhi-kabhi baaz riwayaat ko jisey doosrey Raavi moqufan riwayat kartey hain usey ye marfoo riwayat kar detey hain, 5- mainey Muhammad bin Bashaar ko kehtey huye suna ke abul-Waleed ney kaha : Shoba kehtey hain ke mujh sey Ali bin Zaid ney hadees bayan ki aur Ali bin Zaid Rifaa they, 6- hum Saeed bin Musaiyab ki Anas key wastey sey is lambi hadees key siwa aur koi riwayat nahin jantey , 7- Ibaad bin maisraa Munqari ney ye hadees Ali bin Zaid key wastey sey Anas sey riwayat ki hai, lekin unhoney is hadees mein Saeed bin Musaiyab key wastey ka zikr nahin kya, 8- mainey is hadees ka Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey zikr karkey uskey mutalliq janna chaha to unhoney uskey mutalliq apni la-ilmi ka izhar kya, 9- Anas bin Malik sey Saeed bin Musaiyab ki riwayat sey ye ya iskey ilawa koi bhi hadees maroof nahin hai. Anas bin Malik 93 hijrii mein intiqal farma gaey aur Saeed bin Musaiyab unkey do saal baad 95 hijrii mein Allah ko piyarey huye."
2679,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tak main tumhen chhodey rakhun tum mujhey chhodey rakho, phir jab main tum sey koi chiz bayan karun to usey ley lo, kyonkey tum sey pehley log bahut ziyada sawalat karney aur apney anbiya sey kasrat sey ikhtilafat karney ki wajeh sey halak ho gaey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2680,"''anqareeb aisa waqt aayega ke log ilm ki talash mein kasrat sey lambey-lambey safar tey kerengey, lekin (kahin bhi) unhen Madina key aalim sey bada koi aalim na milega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibn Uena sey marvi ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Sufiyan bin Uena sey us barey mein jab puchha gaya ke aalime-Madina kon hai? to unhoney kaha : Malik bin Anas hain, 3- Is-haq bin Musa kehtey hain : mainey ibn Uena ko kehtey suna ke wo ( yani aalim Madina ( Umri abdul-Azeez bin Abdullah Zahid hain, 4- mainey Yahya bin Musa ko kehtey huye suna abdur-Razzaaq kehtey they ke wo ( aalime-Madina ( Malik bin Anas hain, 5- Umri ye abdul-Azeez bin Abdullah hain, aur ye umr bin Khattab ki aulad mein sey hain."
2681,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' eik faqeeh ( aalim ( hazar ibadat karney walon key muqabley mein akela shetan par hawi aur bhari hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai. hum isey Walid bin Muslim ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain.
2682,"eik shakhs Madina sey Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) key paas dimashq aaya, Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey kaha : merey bhai! tumhen yahan kya chiz ley kar aai hai, usney kaha : mujhey ye baat malum hui hai ke aap Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik hadees bayan kartey hain, Abu-Darda ney kaha : kya tum kisi aur zarurat sey to nahin aaye ho? usney kaha : nahin, unhoney kaha : kya tum tijarat ki gharz sey to nahin aaye ho? usney kaha : nahin, main to sirf is hadees ki talab o talash mein aaya hun, Abu-Darda ney kaha : ( achcha to suno ( mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' jo shakhs ilme-deen ki talash mein kisi raastey par chaley , to Allah Taala uskey zariey usey jannat key raasta par laga deta hai. beshak farishtey Talib ( ilm ( ki khushi key liye apney par bicha detey hain, aur aalim key liye aasman o zamin ki sari makhluqat maghfirat talab karti hain. yahan tak ke pani key andar ki machliyan bhi, aur aalim ki fazilat abid par aisi hi hai jaisey chaand ki fazilat sarey sitaron par , beshak ulama anbiya key waris hain aur anbiya ney kisi ko Dinar o dirham ka waris nahin banaya, balke unhoney ilm ka waris banaya hai. isliye jisney is ilm ko hasil kar liya , usney ( ilm nabawi aur virasate-nabawi sey) pura pura hissey liya '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum Aasim bin Rija bin Hewa ki riwayat key siwa kisi aur tareeq sey is hadees ko nahin jantey , aur is hadees ki sanad merey nazdik muttasil nahin hai. isi tarah inhin asnaad sey Mehmood bin Khaddash ney bhi hum sey bayan ki hai, 2- ye hadees Aasim bin Rija bin Hewa ney b-sanad (داود بن جميل an كثير بن قيس an أبي الدرداء an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai. aur ye hadees Mehmood bin Khaddash ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, aur Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ki raey hai ke ye ziyada sahih hai."
2683,"mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey bahut si hadisein aap sey suni hain, main darta hun ke kahin baad ki hadisein shuru ki hadeeson ko bhula na den, aap mujhey koi aisa kalma (koi aisi baat) bata dijiye jo dono (awwal o aakhir) ko eik sath baqi rakhney ka zaria baney. aap ney farmaya : '' jo kuch bhi tum jantey ho unkey mutalliq Allah ka khof o taqwa malhooz rakho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees aisi hai jiski sanad muttasil nahin hai, ye hadees merey nazdik mursal hai. 2- merey nazdik ibn Ashwaa ney Yazeed bin Salma (key daur) ko nahin paya hai, 3- ibne-Ashwaa ka naam Saeed bin Ashwaa hai."
2684,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' munafiq mein do khaslatein ( siften ( jama nahin ho sakti hain : husney-akhlaq aur Deen ki samajh''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum Auf ki is hadees ko sirf Shekh khalaf bin Ayub Aamiri ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur abu-Kuraib Muhammad bin Alaa key siwa kisi ko hum nahin jantey jisney khalaf bin Ayub Aamiri sey riwayat ki hai, aur hum nahin jantey ke wo kaisey shakhs hain."
2685,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney do aadmiyon ka zikr kya gaya, un mein sey eik abid tha aur doosra aalim , to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aalim ki fazilat abid par aisi hai jaisey meri fazilat tum mein sey eik aam aadmi par hai'' , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah aur uskey farishtey aur aasman aur zamin waley yahan tak ke cheentiyan apni surakh mein aur machliyan us shakhs key liye jo neki o bhalai ki taalim deta hai khair o barkat ki duayen karti hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, 2- Fuzel bin Ayaaz kehtey hain « ملكوت السموات » (aalame-baala) mein amal karney waley aalim aur muallim ko bahut badi ahmiyat o shakhsiyat ka Malik samjha aur pukara jata hai."
2686,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' momin bhalai sey hergiz aasooda nahin hota yahan tak ke wo apney aakhiri anjam jannat mein pahunch jata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2687,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' hikmat ki baat momin ki gumshuda chiz hai jahan kahin bhi usey paey wo usey hasil kar leney ka ziyada haq rakhta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 3- Ibrahim bin Fazal madni makhzoomi hadees bayan karney mein hifz key talluq sey kamzor maaney jatey hain."
